00:10:06,943 --> 00:10:08,343
Apa kita patut buat, Conan?

84
00:10:09,543 --> 00:10:11,942
Kamu pernah cakap apabila FBI pergi dari hospital,

85
00:10:11,943 --> 00:10:14,542
