92
00:10:29,643 --> 00:10:31,042
Saya rasa lebih baik

93
00:10:31,043 --> 00:10:32,942
saya balik dan tidur.

94
00:10:32,943 --> 00:10:35,342
Jumpa lagi, Jodie.

95
00:10:35,343 --> 00:10:38,342
Hari Jumaat, 13 hari bulan.

96
00:10:38,343 --> 00:10:40,842
Apa?

97
00:10:40,843 --> 00:10:42,143
Hati-hati.

98
00:10:44,043 --> 00:10:47,542
Saya rasa tak sedap hati hari ini.

99
00:10:47,543 --> 00:10:51,143
Kerana hari ini ialah hari Jumaat, 13 hari bulan, bukan?

100
00:10:53,243 --> 00:10:56,543
Saya tak percaya perkara begitu.

101
00:10:57,943 --> 00:11:00,243
Begitu rupanya.

102
00:11:06,709 --> 00:11:07,908
Apa?

103
00:11:07,909 --> 00:11:12,008
