104
00:11:12,009 --> 00:11:13,009
Ya.

105
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:18,408
Dia menerima panggilan daripada Rena selepas kamu pergi.

106
00:11:18,409 --> 00:11:20,508
Dia kata hendak berjumpa Rena. Mereka berdua saja.

107
00:11:20,509 --> 00:11:22,008
Mereka berdua saja...

108
00:11:22,009 --> 00:11:24,108
Saya yakin itu satu perangkap!

109
00:11:24,109 --> 00:11:26,708
Kenapa kamu tak halang dia?

110
00:11:26,709 --> 00:11:29,108
Sebenarnya saya sudah menghalangnya.

111
00:11:29,109 --> 00:11:30,408
Dia berkeras yang dia perlu pergi

112
00:11:30,409 --> 00:11:33,508
