115
00:11:37,809 --> 00:11:40,108
Itu...

116
00:11:40,109 --> 00:11:44,008
Mereka akan berjumpa di Jalan Raiha, bukan?

117
00:11:44,009 --> 00:11:45,508
Ya.

118
00:11:45,509 --> 00:11:48,908
Saya menonton berita di televisyen tadi

119
00:11:48,909 --> 00:11:51,708
bahawa ada sebuah kereta terbakar di Jalan Raiha

120
00:11:51,709 --> 00:11:54,408
dan nampaknya ada mayat terbakar yang ditemui di dalam.

121
00:11:54,409 --> 00:11:56,009
-Apa? -Apa?

122
00:11:57,209 --> 00:11:59,508
