219
00:17:03,609 --> 00:17:05,208
Jadi...

220
00:17:05,209 --> 00:17:10,408
Sekarang kita sudah berjaya menusuk baji ke dalam Organisasi.

221
00:17:10,409 --> 00:17:13,409
